</container>
</locomotive>
</wheeled_vehicle>
</instrumentality>
</artifact>
</self-propelled_vehicle>
</conveyance>
 <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../492/346492.xml">
shunter</link>.</p>
<p>

In 1992, <link>
Model Iber S.A.</link>, the company from Barcelona behind the Ibertren brand, was forced to shut down<ref xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="#xpointer(//reflist/entry[@id=%222%22])">2</ref> due to financial problems.</p>
<p>

In 2004, a company named "Ibertren Modelismo, S.L." (also from Barcelona) relaunched the brand, with a HO-only catalog<ref xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="#xpointer(//reflist/entry[@id=%223%22])">3</ref>.</p>
